<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-family: Helvetica; color: rgb(54, 125, 162);  ">桃园机场睡觉地之3楼躺椅区</p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Helvetica;   min-height: 18px;"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-156-4.jpg" title="桃园机场免费睡觉地盘点_图片_4" alt="桃园机场免费睡觉地盘点_图片_4"></p>
<p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 15px; font-family: Helvetica;  ">外观相当隐蔽大休息去，有10张以上休息躺椅，离各登机室不远，想购物或取款都很方便。</p>
